rd PHRASE (never a whole sentence, never the words "click here", "buy now", "here" or "this link"); vary the wording across the four placements; use markdown syntax [anchor](SHOPIFY_URL) or [anchor](AFFILIATE_URL) with those literal tokens.\n${tone}\nBritish English throughout.`;
